graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelMesh -->|metadata & routing| etcd[etcd v3.2+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|model artifacts| S3[S3/MinIO Object Storage<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|manage resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelMesh -.->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ModelMesh -.->|mTLS & routing| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -->|metrics export| MonitoringStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus Operator v0.50+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|model references| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    subgraph Runtimes["Supported Model Runtimes"]
        Triton[Triton Inference Server<br/>tritonserver-2:latest<br/>TF, PyTorch, ONNX, TensorRT]
        MLServer[MLServer<br/>mlserver-1:latest<br/>SKLearn, XGBoost, MLflow]
        OVMS[OpenVINO Model Server<br/>ovms-1:latest<br/>OpenVINO IR, ONNX, TF]
        TorchServe[TorchServe<br/>torchserve-0:latest<br/>PyTorch, TorchScript]
    end

    ModelMesh -->|deploys| Triton
    ModelMesh -->|deploys| MLServer
    ModelMesh -->|deploys| OVMS
    ModelMesh -->|deploys| TorchServe

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management]
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Auto-deployment]

    Dashboard -.->|manages via UI| ModelMesh
    Pipelines -.->|deploys models| ModelMesh

    %% Styling
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (required)
    style etcd fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style S3 fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (optional)
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH dependencies
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style MonitoringStack fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000

    %% Runtimes
    style Triton fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style MLServer fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style OVMS fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style TorchServe fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000

    %% Integration points
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
